➜劝都劝不住！村民哄抢榴莲后，剧情出现反转
http://www.sohu.com/a/415364030_423465	33158
<p class="ql-align-center">8月26日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">广西一艘装满榴莲的货船侧翻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>当地村民和游客不听劝阻执意哄抢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果事情出现反转</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>捡了榴莲吃的人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>出现腹痛、呕吐、腹泻……</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>榴莲货船侧翻遭村民哄抢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>劝都劝不住</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据一名知情村民介绍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">事发地为广西防城港市万尾金滩海域</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当天早上7点多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">距离岸边约200米处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一艘满载榴莲的铁皮船侧翻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>船上的榴莲全部漂到海面</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有的还漂在海滩上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>绵延约有1公里长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当地村民和游客见状</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纷纷下海打捞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随后用车拉回家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目击者介绍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“估计有上百人在现场打捞榴莲”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/9f29ba3e3c804233862d2600f2f9d350.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
